# AtlasBR

AtlasBR is an AI-powered ecosystem that brings together news automation, predictive analytics, employment intelligence, market monitoring and business tools in a single platform.

Built with artificial intelligence and automation at its core, AtlasBR transforms large volumes of public and market data into practical insights for businesses, entrepreneurs and consumers.

## Core Features

- Atlas News AI
- Atlas Radar Marketplace Intelligence
- Atlas Pulse Employment Forecasting
- Predictive Weather Analysis
- PIX Cost Simulator
- Intelligent RSS Aggregation
- AI Agent Integration

